Project: camel-spring-bean-rs-api
Description: This is exposing rest end points using camel. This project is following spring dsl approach.

Services:

Welcome service:
Verb: GET
Content-Type: text/plain 
Endpoint URL: http://localhost:8080/camel/welcome

Save student service accepts json request:
Verb: POST
Content-Type: application/json
Endpoint URL: http://localhost:8080/camel/saveStudent

Request example:

{
  "id": "101",
  "grade": "B",
  "name": "Sam Wood",
  "marks": 65.78
}

Save student service accepts xml request:
Verb: POST
Content-Type: application/xml
Endpoint URL: http://localhost:8080/camel/saveStudentXml

Request example:
<studentxml>
	<id>1000</id>
	<name>name</name>
	<address>Address</address>
</studentxml>
